dataset_id: GPM GMI RSS Common Calibrated Brightness Temperatures L1BASE 1.5 hours 13 km V05 (GPM_BASEGPMGMI_RSS) at GES DISC
title: GPM GMI RSS Common Calibrated Brightness Temperatures L1BASE 1.5 hours 13 km V05 (GPM_BASEGPMGMI_RSS) at GES DISC
summary:
Version 5 is the current version of the data set. Version 4 is no longer available and has been superseded by Version 5.

This GPM GMI contains  "GMI Antenna Temperatures", and is written as a multi-Swath Structure. Swath S1 has channels 1-9: 10V 10H 19V 19H 23V 37V 37H 89V 89H. Swath S2 has channels 10-13: 166V 166H 183+/-3V 183+/-8V. GMIBASERSS is like GMIBASE but has an overlap of 200 scans on each end.
